{"type":"message","id":"4a4260e1","parentId":"5d3abdbb","timestamp":"2026-05-03T18:05:32.981Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:750f75a2-47fc-4a2d-b986-9557c0ddd4ae Wiki Logging - DJ] Execute: python3 ~/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-heartbeat.py dj\n\nThis logs recent conversations to the wiki at ~/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/daily-logs/. Read the wiki-heartbeat.py script and follow its logic.\nCurrent time: Sunday, May 3rd, 2026 - 2:05 PM (America/New_York) / 2026-05-03 18:05 UTC"}],"timestamp":1777831532930}}
